{"tid":2191674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"多名工作中的九巴職員被警方以限聚令要求他們離開，不要再逗留彌敦道一帶，並指他們已違法。","createTime":"2020-09-06T14:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T03:36:44.000Z","uid":222970,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c07d70e456c419e57d1ac24fb879dce54e707f3b","tid":2191674,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V3ZNSzy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV3ZNSzy.jpg&h=e607cb2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九巴員工指，他們由公司委派負責匯報彌敦道行車狀況。未幾幾名九巴員工被警方以限聚令要求他們離開，不要再逗留彌敦道一帶，並指他們已違法。其後九巴亦有車輛到場了解情況，警方只作出警告並要求離開，警告不能2人以上聚集。<br />\n<br />\n撰 ／ Jar<br />\n圖 ／ Jar<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n​<br />\n香城公民媒體 ​<br />\nHong Kong Citizen Media​<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkcitizenmedia.com/​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkcitizenmedia.com%2F%E2%80%8B&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4qVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=bf18033f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkcitizenmedia.com/​</a><br />\n​<br />\nFacebook：​<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HK.CitizenMedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHK.CitizenMedia%2F&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4qVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=7d76826e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HK.CitizenMedia/</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram：​<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hk.citizenmedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhk.citizenmedia%2F&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4qVNHo2TAuuzEKoC36QvVjA%3D&h=5107f71b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hk.citizenmedia/</a><br />\n<br />\n#香城公民媒體 #hongkongcitizenmedia #hkcitizenmedia #公民媒體 #新聞自由 #公義 #CitizenJournalist #HongKongCulture #香港加油 #media #hongkongers #hkphoto #homekong #